OL,3,CWatchdog opens new probe into Thames
OL,4,CWater over delays to environmental work
OL,6,FWater regulator Ofwat has launched an
OL,7,Finvestigation into Thames Water over
OL,8,Fconcerns it will not complete more
OL,9,Fthan 100 environmental schemes funded
OL,10,Fby customers.
OL,12,FThe regulator said it will probe
OL,13,Fwhether delays to the plans mean
OL,14,FEngland's largest water firm has
OL,15,Fbreached its licence.
OL,17,FThe schemes were aimed at making
OL,18,Fimprovements to water companies'
OL,19,Fenvironmental impact, such as through
OL,20,Fupgrades to sewage treatment works and
OL,21,Freducing wastewater spillages.
