OL,3,CWatchdog opens new probe into Thames
OL,4,CWater over delays to environmental work
OL,6,FThames Water pledged to carry out 812
OL,7,Fschemes as part of a wider national
OL,8,Fprogramme between 2020 and 2025, to
OL,9,Fmeet national regulations.
OL,11,FBut Ofwat said it was told by the
OL,12,Futilities giant that it would be
OL,13,Funlikely to complete more than 100 of
OL,14,Fthese schemes by the end of March
OL,15,Fdeadline.
OL,17,FLynn Parker, senior director for
OL,18,Fenforcement at Ofwat, said: "Customers
OL,19,Fhave paid for Thames Water to carry
OL,20,Fout these essential environmental
OL,21,Fschemes.
