OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F415A1739439975
OL,3,CWatchdog opens new probe into Thames
OL,4,CWater over delays to environmental work
OL,6,F"We take any indication that water
OL,7,Fcompanies are not meeting their legal
OL,8,Fobligations very seriously.
OL,10,F"Therefore, we have launched an
OL,11,Finvestigation to understand whether
OL,12,Fthe delayed delivery of environmental
OL,13,Fschemes means that Thames Water has
OL,14,Fbreached its obligations.
OL,16,F"If we find reason to act, we will use
OL,17,Four full range of powers to hold
OL,18,FThames to account for any failures and
OL,19,Fwill require them to put things right."
