OL,3,CWatchdog opens new probe into Thames
OL,4,CWater over delays to environmental work
OL,6,FA spokeswoman for Thames Water said
OL,7,Fthe company will "co-operate fully"
OL,8,Fwith Ofwat, stressing: "Customers will
OL,9,Fnot pay twice for investment that has
OL,10,Falready been funded through customer
OL,11,Fbills."
OL,13,FShe added that Thames Water has been
OL,14,F"very open about the challenges of
OL,15,Fdelivering all the elements" of its
OL,16,Fprogramme, "which has been impacted by
OL,17,Fcost increases that are higher than
OL,18,Fthe inflation index applied to our
OL,19,Fallowances".
