OL,6,FLiberal Democrat MP Charlie Maynard
OL,7,Fsaid the investigation was the "last
OL,8,Fnail in the coffin" for the firm,
OL,9,Fadding: "Customers across London and
OL,10,Fthe South East deserve better."
OL,12,F"The Government has a choice to do the
OL,13,Fright thing and put this failing
OL,14,Fcompany into special administration,"
OL,15,Fhe said.
